IN RE MARION/MARTINEZ, Minors. SC: 158222
COA: 341428 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 24, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the July 19, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
